// Example BuritoJava program exercising:
//   - FinalVarDeclaration (desugared in output)
//   - Complex expressions as operands (normalized to temps)
//   - Return Expression (normalized to identifier)
//   - If/While with expression conditions
//   - MessageSend with expression arguments
//   - AndExpression / ORExpression (expanded to if-else)
//   - BracketExpression (unwrapped)
